divs: Sighting DetailsThere was no object above the hotel when i made this photo,It was a clear day only after down loading the photos did i see this object. The photos that when taken before and after do not show this object.There was three photos taken and only one shows this object, all the photos where taken with in seconds of each other.We where traveling down highway 101 southbound and I thought it would be nice to take some photos of the hotel only to find out later that there was an object above the hotel in one of the photos.
